{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|1Co|2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","chapter":2,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":1,"text":"When I came to you, brothers and sisters, announcing the mystery of God to you, I did not come with brilliance of speech or wisdom.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":2,"text":"I decided to know nothing among you except Jesus Christ and him crucified.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":3,"text":"I came to you in weakness, in fear, and in much trembling.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":4,"text":"My speech and my preaching were not with persuasive words of wisdom but with a demonstration of the Spirit’s power,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":5,"text":"so that your faith might not be based on human wisdom but on God’s power.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":6,"text":"We do, however, speak a wisdom among the mature, but not a wisdom of this age, or of the rulers of this age, who are coming to nothing.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":7,"text":"On the contrary, we speak God’s hidden wisdom in a mystery, a wisdom God predestined before the ages for our glory.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":8,"text":"None of the rulers of this age knew this wisdom, because if they had known it, they would not have crucified the Lord of glory.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":9,"text":"But as it is written,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":10,"text":"Now God has revealed these things to us by the Spirit, since the Spirit searches everything, even the depths of God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":11,"text":"For who knows a person’s thoughts except his spirit within him? In the same way, no one knows the thoughts of God except the Spirit of God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":12,"text":"Now we have not received the spirit of the world, but the Spirit who comes from God, so that we may understand what has been freely given to us by God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":13,"text":"We also speak these things, not in words taught by human wisdom, but in those taught by the Spirit, explaining spiritual things to spiritual people.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":14,"text":"But the person without the Spirit does not receive what comes from God’s Spirit, because it is foolishness to him; he is not able to understand it since it is evaluated spiritually.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":15,"text":"The spiritual person, however, can evaluate everything, and yet he himself cannot be evaluated by anyone.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":2,"verse":16,"text":"For But we have the mind of Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","chapter":2,"paragraphStarts":[1,6,10],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Paul’s Proclamation"},{"beforeVerse":6,"text":"Spiritual Wisdom"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When I came to you, brothers and sisters, announcing the mystery "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read testimony"},{"kind":"text","text":" of God to you, I did not come with brilliance "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 2:2","book":"1Ti","chapter":2,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" of speech "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 4:6","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" or wisdom. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Tm 2:2","book":"1Ti","chapter":2,"verse":2},{"label":"Col 4:6","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read testimony"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I decided to know nothing among you except Jesus Christ and him crucified. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:23–24","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 6:14","book":"Gal","chapter":6,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 1:23–24","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":23},{"label":"Gl 6:14","book":"Gal","chapter":6,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I came to you in weakness, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 11:30","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":30,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" in fear, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 11:11","book":"Rev","chapter":11,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and in much trembling. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:12","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Co 11:30","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":30},{"label":"Rv 11:11","book":"Rev","chapter":11,"verse":11},{"label":"Php 2:12","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"My speech "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 12:37","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":37,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and my preaching were not with persuasive "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:25","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" words of wisdom "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss read human wisdom"},{"kind":"text","text":" but with a demonstration of the Spirit’s power, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 12:37","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":37},{"label":"Php 1:25","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss read human wisdom"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"so that your faith might not be based on human wisdom but on God’s power. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 5:30","book":"Mrk","chapter":5,"verse":30,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 1:35","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":35,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 6:19","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":19,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 19:11","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":11,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 13:4","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":4,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 1:7","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 11:17","book":"Rev","chapter":11,"verse":17,"letter":"g"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 5:30","book":"Mrk","chapter":5,"verse":30},{"label":"Lk 1:35","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":35},{"label":"Lk 6:19","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":19},{"label":"Ac 19:11","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":11},{"label":"2Co 13:4","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":4},{"label":"2Tm 1:7","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":7},{"label":"Rv 11:17","book":"Rev","chapter":11,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"We do, however, speak a wisdom among the mature, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:48","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":48,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" but not a wisdom of this age, or of the rulers "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:58","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":58,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" of this age, who are coming to nothing. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 2:14","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":14,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 5:48","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":48},{"label":"Lk 12:58","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":58},{"label":"Heb 2:14","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On the contrary, we speak God’s hidden wisdom in a mystery, a wisdom God predestined "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:5","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" before the ages for our glory. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 24:26","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 5:1","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 5:4","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":4,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Eph 1:5","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":5},{"label":"Lk 24:26","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":26},{"label":"1Pt 5:1","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":1},{"label":"1Pt 5:4","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"None of the rulers of this age knew this wisdom, because if they had known it, they would not have crucified the Lord of glory. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 24:7","book":"Psa","chapter":24,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 24:7","book":"Psa","chapter":24,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But as it is written,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now God has revealed these things to us by the Spirit, since the Spirit searches everything, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 17:3","book":"Psa","chapter":17,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 14:26","book":"Jhn","chapter":14,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" even the depths of God. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:39","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":39,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 11:33","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":33,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 3:18","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":18,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 17:3","book":"Psa","chapter":17,"verse":3},{"label":"Jn 14:26","book":"Jhn","chapter":14,"verse":26},{"label":"Rm 8:39","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":39},{"label":"Rm 11:33","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":33},{"label":"Eph 3:18","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For who knows a person’s thoughts "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or things"},{"kind":"text","text":" except his spirit "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:9","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" within him? In the same way, no one knows "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 4:8","book":"1Jn","chapter":4,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" the thoughts of God except the Spirit of God. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 1:9","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":9},{"label":"1Jn 4:8","book":"1Jn","chapter":4,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or things"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now we have not received the spirit of the world, but the Spirit who comes from God, so that we may understand what has been freely given to us by God. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"We also speak these things, not in words "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 12:37","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":37,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" taught by human wisdom, but in those taught by the Spirit, explaining spiritual things to spiritual people. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or things with spiritual words"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 12:37","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":37}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or things with spiritual words"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But the person without the Spirit "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Lit natural person"},{"kind":"text","text":" does not receive what comes from God’s Spirit, because it is foolishness to him; he is not able to understand it since it is evaluated "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":4,"text":"Or judged, or discerned, also in v. 15"},{"kind":"text","text":" spiritually. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Lit natural person"},{"marker":4,"text":"Or judged, or discerned, also in v. 15"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The spiritual person, however, can evaluate "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":5,"text":"Or judge, or discern"},{"kind":"text","text":" everything, and yet he himself cannot be evaluated by anyone. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":5,"text":"Or judge, or discern"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:2:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For"},{"kind":"text","text":" But we have the mind of Christ. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 2:2","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":2,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Col 2:2","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279657184}